PerfectMoney,offers,a,secure,money,transfer,service,from,p,p,and,from,b,b,The,PerfectMoney,API,allows,users,to,interact,with,the,PerfectMoney,service,programmatically,using,the,REST,protocol,The,API,allows,users,to,check,account,history,balance,exchange,rates,and,e,voucher,listings,of,the,user,s,account,It,also,enables,active,uses,such,as,spending,calls,and,e,Voucher,creation